properties.name: Carol Miller
properties.biography: Carol Miller earned a bachelor's degree in history and political science from Columbia College in 1972. Her career experience includes working as a self-employed real estate manager since 1985. She has owned Swann Ridge Bison Farm since 1994. Miller ran for the West Virginia House of Delegates in 2004 but was not elected. Miller was elected to represent West Virginia's District 15 seat in 2006 and held that seat until being redistricted to District 16 in the 2012 election. As of 2018, Miller was the majority whip in the state House of Delegates.
